    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is any statement to be made on the question whether this disaster is the result of tempest or flood?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9a4246f6-8dd0-4ff6-8b5b-46b3379d0e4f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
