            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a58d20e4-c167-4f87-836a-c95b0c0c6f11" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
