            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8a160bc4-e1b4-4e5d-9615-58973f0eac71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
