    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I only wish to point out that, if the right hon. Gentleman knew his job as Minister of Local Government, he would know that he is the Minister who has authority to remit the surcharge.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7b5d689a-ac9a-4d24-b0f0-2e310a7e3215" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-02-19/debates/27c6a253-4ffb-42ac-9e48-741edd8f1281/FloodDisasters#contribution-7b5d689a-ac9a-4d24-b0f0-2e310a7e3215">
